title: Episode 157 w/ Cesar (Flipping NJ), Doug (Netflix), DC Family
itunes:title: Episode 157 w/ Cesar (Flipping NJ), Doug (Netflix), DC Family
description:
N.O.R.E & DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. On this special episode the Champs link up with the DC Family at Circle House Studios and interview Cesar, who's a real estate mogul, on ways to invest and make money in the real estate game. Also interview Doug, who is a producer at Netflix, and talk about what he does and how it is working alongside Will Smith.
